summary: After having accomplished my studies Italian at Utrecht University, my father -cinema exibitor in Enschede- fell ill and I had to replace him. My fiancee - my husband now - joined me to reorganise and enlarge the company. Meanwhile I improved my skills in languages: French, German, English and at the same time my knowledge of fashion by reading magazines,visiting and working in boutiques of the newest brands. After our departure in 2006 from the cinemabusiness I develloped a system as personal shopper and fashion advisor for people who had problems with deciding ans choosing their wardrobe, as a private entrepreneur. At the same time giving language lessons.
